comprises two allopatric species, 
<taxonomicName box="[838,983,1368,1392]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Gobiidae" genus="Lotilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageId="1" pageNumber="55" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="graciliosa">
